    </div>
    <div class="card" onclick="showSection('galaxies')" style="text-align:center;padding:32px 20px">
      <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:12px">🌌</div>
      <div class="card-name" style="margin-bottom:8px">Galaxies</div>
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7">Spiral, elliptical, and irregular galaxies. Each linked to known black holes and exoplanets.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

